<div class="com-share" data-id="6092" data-title="《创始人名字命名的公司更容易失败？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6092/medium/6092.png?1436692941" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6092.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
